data.description: Sought after East Sparks location sets the backdrop for your perfect starter, downsized, or investment home! Perfect for entertaining, this popular floor plan flows invitingly from entry into the spacious great room & seamlessly connects the dining, kitchen & covered outdoor patio. Your Master Retreat boasts custom walk in closet, oversized counter & VIEWS! You’ll enjoy vibrant mountain sunsets over downtown Reno every night! Unbeatable location within walking distance to both necessities & amenities. Situated in an established neighborhood with mature landscaping and zoned for popular schools, this neighborhood is highly desired for it’s close proximity to shopping, entertainment, and leisure including many city parks and public lands walking trails. The backyard provides an oversized covered patio perfect for outdoor entertainment and relaxation. The back perimeter is adorned with rose bushes that bloom beautifully in the Spring and Summer. The kitchen is thoughtfully updated boasting custom oak cabinets, and granite counters with waterfall edges and matching full coverage granite backsplash. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for guests, roommates, a home office, or growing family. A convenient half bathroom is located on the main floor for guests. This home also offers tons of storage with built in shelving in the garage plus plenty of closets throughout including an extra storage closet under the stairs. Schedule your private showing today!
